OL,3,CHospital must address culture and
OL,4,Cleadership issues, inspectors warn
OL,6,FBosses of a Brighton hospital must
OL,7,Faddress issues over its culture and
OL,8,Fleadership at an "urgent pace", health
OL,9,Finspectors have warned.
OL,11,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,12,Frevealed the culture in surgery
OL,13,Ftheatres at Royal Sussex County
OL,14,FHospital was "still poor", and that
OL,15,Fstaff did not feel they could raise
OL,16,Fconcerns without "fear of reprisals".
