OL,3,CHospital must address culture and
OL,4,Cleadership issues, inspectors warn
OL,6,FThe unannounced visit in August 2023
OL,7,Ffound an "improving" culture on the
OL,8,Fwards where staff felt respected and
OL,9,Fsupported, but inspectors also heard
OL,10,Fexamples of bullying in the surgery
OL,11,Funit from 30 members of staff.
OL,13,FCQC bosses said improvements had been
OL,14,Fmade in some aspects of surgery at the
OL,15,Fhospital since inspections in 2021 and
OL,16,F2022, resulting in the unit being
OL,17,Fraised from an "inadequate" rating to
OL,18,F"requires improvement".
