OL,3,CHospital must address culture and
OL,4,Cleadership issues, inspectors warn
OL,6,FThe CQC inspection report which was
OL,7,Fpublished today (14 February) focused
OL,8,Fon surgical services and medical care.
OL,10,FIt said: "Not all theatre staff felt
OL,11,Frespected, supported, and valued.
OL,12,FStaff in theatres did not feel they
OL,13,Fcould raise concerns without fear of
OL,14,Freprisals.
OL,16,F"However, there was an improving
OL,17,Fculture on the wards where staff felt
OL,18,Frespected, supported and valued. Staff
OL,19,Fwere focused on the needs of patients
OL,20,Freceiving care across all environments.
