OL,3,CHospital must address culture and
OL,4,Cleadership issues, inspectors warn
OL,6,F"We spoke with 30 members of staff who
OL,7,Fgave us examples of bullying in the
OL,8,Funit with a divided workforce and a
OL,9,Fperception that some staff were
OL,10,Ftreated differently to others.
OL,12,F"Staff told us they were placed in
OL,13,Fdifficult circumstances daily and they
OL,14,Fdid not feel listened to when they
OL,15,Freported these concerns."
