OL,6,FConcerns were also raised over waiting
OL,7,Ftimes getting worse and cancellations
OL,8,Fof surgery, due to staffing and
OL,9,Fcapacity in theatres.Inspectors said
OL,10,Fone patient they spoke to had her
OL,11,Forthopaedic surgery cancelled eight
OL,12,Ftimes in a row.
OL,14,FThe trust overall was put in the
OL,15,Flowest 25% of NHS acute trusts in the
OL,16,FSouth East for national cancer waiting
OL,17,Ftime data, achieving 66% for two-week
OL,18,Fwaits, compared to the 93% national
OL,19,Ftarget.
