OL,3,CHospital must address culture and
OL,4,Cleadership issues, inspectors warn
OL,6,FCQC inspectors also reviewed other
OL,7,Fhospitals managed by the trust,
OL,8,FPrincess Royal Hospital in Haywards
OL,9,FHeath, St Richard's Hospital in
OL,10,FChichester and Worthing Hospital, with
OL,11,Fthe trust overall maintaining a rating
OL,12,Fof "requires improvement".
OL,14,FOverall, CQC deputy director of
OL,15,Foperations in the South, Neil Cox,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Following our previous
OL,17,Finspection of University Hospitals
OL,18,FSussex NHS Foundation Trust, we told
OL,19,Fthem where they needed to make
OL,20,Fimprovements especially around
OL,21,Fleadership and culture.
