OL,3,CHospital must address culture and
OL,4,Cleadership issues, inspectors warn
OL,6,F"At this inspection whilst we found
OL,7,Fimprovements in some areas, other
OL,8,Fissues remained. Leaders must address
OL,9,Fthese issues at a much more urgent
OL,10,Fpace.
OL,12,F"We found a wide disconnect in the
OL,13,Frelationship between staff and senior
OL,14,Fleaders and how they were working
OL,15,Ftogether. These issues were clearly
OL,16,Fhaving a knock-on effect on the
OL,17,Fquality of care being delivered to
OL,18,Fpeople using services."
