OL,6,FHe added there were some improvements
OL,7,Finto the culture in theatres raised in
OL,8,Fprevious inspections and that the
OL,9,Ftrust was taking steps to support
OL,10,Fstaff speaking up despite low staff
OL,11,Fmorale and bullying.But the health
OL,12,Fboss also said inspectors saw some
OL,13,F"exceptionally caring" staff go above
OL,14,Fand beyond to ensure people had
OL,15,Fpositive experiences in hospital.
