OL,3,CHospital must address culture and
OL,4,Cleadership issues, inspectors warn
OL,6,FMr Cox said: "We saw staff taking home
OL,7,Fone person's clothes and washing them
OL,8,Fas they had no family, ensuring
OL,9,Fsomeone's favourite biscuits were
OL,10,Favailable despite it not being a
OL,11,Fstandard item, and bringing in nail
OL,12,Fpolish so someone's relative could
OL,13,Fpaint their nails for them.
OL,15,F"Staff were consistently asking people
OL,16,Fabout their personal, cultural and
OL,17,Freligious needs and understood how to
OL,18,Fincorporate this into their care."
