OL,11,FResponding to the report, Dr George
OL,12,FFindlay, Chief Executive, University
OL,13,FHospitals Sussex Foundation Trust
OL,14,Fsaid: "The CQC inspection team found
OL,15,Ffrontline teams giving good patient
OL,16,Fcare, treating patients with kindness
OL,17,Fand respect, and working well together.
