OL,6,F"Those are fundamental strengths, and
OL,7,Fit is to their enormous credit that
OL,8,Fthey are giving such good care in such
OL,9,Fdifficult circumstances.
OL,11,F"But the CQC also found too many
OL,12,Fthings that we need to do better `
OL,13,Ffrom more consistent record-keeping to
OL,14,Ftraining, to managing pressures on
OL,15,Foverstretched staff, improving our
OL,16,Fculture, and in some of our hospitals,
OL,17,Fmaking colleagues feel more confident
OL,18,Fto speak up.
OL,20,F"We accept those challenges and we are
OL,21,Fworking hard to put them right."
